# Definition of Ready (DoR)

A beads task may **not** enter Phase 7 (Developer) until all items hold:

- [ ] Acceptance criteria copied on the `br` issue
- [ ] Edge cases listed in REQ (from Phase 2 grilling)
- [ ] File map feasible — no "TBD" implementation paths
- [ ] No **blocking** open technical questions (Phase 6 plan)
- [ ] Infrastructure impact known (devops section when applicable)
- [ ] Lane tagged on issue: `flow: full|fast|short`

If DoR fails, coordinator loops back to Phase 6 (Team Lead).

